column2: SELECT     m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1,     n.specObjID, n.distance,     s.ra AS ra2, s.dec AS dec2,    s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning,    s.survey, s.instrument, s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.class,    s.legacy_target1, s.legacy_target2, s.primTarget, s.secTarget,    s.boss_target1, s.eboss_target0, s.eboss_target1, s.eboss_target2,    s.special_target1, s.special_target2,    s.ancillary_target1, s.ancillary_target2 FROM MyDB.mFNoptRADEC AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN SpecObj AS s ON n.specObjID=s.specObjID INTO MyDB.mFNoptSpec
